	"metadata": {
		"inclusion": "1. Power the device.\n2. Quickly, triple click the button on the device housing or a switch connected to IN1 or IN2.\n3. The LED will start blinking yellow.",
		"exclusion": "1. Power the device.\n2. Quickly, triple click the button on the device housing or a switch connected to IN1 or IN2.\n3. The LED will start blinking yellow.",
		"reset": "1. Press and hold the button to enter the menu.\n2. Release the button when the device glows yellow.\n3. Quickly click the button to confirm.\n4. After a few seconds the device restarts, which is signaled by the LED glowing red.",
		"manual": "https://manuals.fibaro.com/content/manuals/en/FGBS-222/FGBS-222-T-EN-rev.1.2.6.pdf"
